+# Phase 01-02 Plan: Privacy UX, Auditability, and Deny-Path Messaging
+
+## Objective
+Deliver user-visible trust controls and evidence surfaces, including explicit messaging when users deny remote inference.
+
+## Context
+- `.planning/phases/01-local-first-core-privacy-guardrails/01-CONTEXT.md`
+- `.planning/phases/01-local-first-core-privacy-guardrails/01-RESEARCH.md`
+- `.planning/phases/01-local-first-core-privacy-guardrails/01-01-PLAN.md`
+
