+  <must_have id="MH-04" requirement="PRIV-02">Any response produced through remote inference displays an explicit badge and short reason.</must_have>
+  <must_have id="MH-05" requirement="PRIV-02">When remote inference is denied, system returns local-only result with explicit note that remote could improve output.</must_have>
+</must_haves>
